- OH, WELL, I WOULDN'T KNOW,

11:19.400 --> 11:20.298
BECAUSE WE'VE NEVER HAD ONE.

11:20.400 --> 11:21.799
- MM-HMM.
THAT'S RIGHT.

11:21.920 --> 11:23.080
AND WE SHOULD NEVER HAVE ONE.

11:23.190 --> 11:24.532
