OFFICIALLY OLD AND MARRIED.

11:33.620 --> 11:34.928
- WELL, WE ARE OLD AND MARRIED.

11:35.030 --> 11:36.964
- WELL, MAYBE YOU'RE OLD
AND MARRIED--I'M NOT.

11:37.070 --> 11:39.482
I'M IN A HOT, STEAMY
RELATIONSHIP THAT SOMETIMES ENDS

11:39.590 --> 11:42.241
ON THE FLOOR OF THIS KITCHEN.
- OOH, NOW THAT IS FUNKYTOWN.

11:42.350 --> 11:44.102
