THE NEXT DAY.

12:08.550 --> 12:10.063
- I MEAN,
WE COULD BE THOSE PEOPLE

12:10.170 --> 12:11.341
THAT CAN'T BREAK ANY RULES,

12:11.450 --> 12:12.109
OR WE COULD BE THE PEOPLE

12:12.210 --> 12:14.622
THAT EAT THE SALMON TOMORROW,

12:14.730 --> 12:15.583
TONIGHT WE DO PIZZA.

12:15.700 --> 12:16.769
- YEAH.
