- HEY, DAD, MOM SAID
WE'RE GETTING A DOG.

13:03.990 --> 13:05.366
- WHAT?
- I NEVER SAID THAT.

13:05.470 --> 13:06.744
- AND THIS IS THE ONE I WANT.
- WHEN DID THIS--HONEY.

13:06.850 --> 13:08.226
- COME HERE, LOOK.
- HE'S DOING RESEARCH.

13:08.330 --> 13:09.843
- SHE'S A GOLDEN RETRIEVER.
- GREAT-LOOKING DOG.

13:09.960 --> 13:12.576
- SEE, GOLDEN RETRIEVERS
WERE FIRST BRED IN SCOTLAND.

13:12.680 --> 13:15.888
THEY'RE A MIX BETWEEN
WATER SPANIELS AND LABRADORS.

13:16.000 --> 13:17.160
AND, NOW, THE REASON
THEY'RE CALLED RETRIEVERS

13:17.270 --> 13:19.022
IS BECAUSE MEN
WOULD GO OUT HUNTING.

13:19.140 --> 13:20.368
YOU SEE, THEY WOULD SHOOT
THE BIRDS,

13:20.480 --> 13:21.651
AND SOMETIMES THE BIRDS
WOULD FALL INTO THE POND.

13:21.760 --> 13:23.068
THEY WOULD NEED A COOL DOG

13:23.180 --> 13:25.387
TO BE ABLE TO GO SWIM
AND RETRIEVE THEM, YOU SEE.

13:25.490 --> 13:26.764
- OKAY, LET'S JUST SLOW DOWN
FOR A SECOND, BUDDY.

13:27.870 --> 13:29.724
NOW, MOM,
WE ARE LOOKING AT DOGS.

13:29.840 --> 13:31.068
