GETTING A DOG.

13:59.420 --> 14:00.899
- YEAH, YOU SAID THAT YOU AND
DAD TALKED ABOUT GETTING A DOG.

14:01.010 --> 14:01.726
- WE SPOKE--
- THIS IS IT.

14:01.840 --> 14:03.523
THIS IS THE ONE I WANT.

14:03.630 --> 14:05.040
DAD, THIS DOG,
IT'S AMAZING.

14:05.150 --> 14:06.629
WE'RE GETTING
THIS DOG TOMORROW.

14:06.740 --> 14:07.593
- MAX.
- YES!

14:07.700 --> 14:08.735
- OH, MY GOD, MAX.
HONEY.

14:08.840 --> 14:10.979
