17:24.490 --> 17:26.822
- YOU ARE GOING TO SHOW HER.

17:26.940 --> 17:29.079
- SHOW HER WHAT?

17:29.180 --> 17:31.694
- YOU MEAN, YOUR INTENT
ON ACQUIRING ONE

17:31.800 --> 17:34.041
OF THESE CHAMPIONSHIP STOCK

17:34.150 --> 17:35.458
