INTO A HOUSEHOLD PET?

17:35.570 --> 17:39.563
- YEAH, WELL,
IT'S A DOG, ISN'T IT?

17:39.670 --> 17:41.979
- NO?

17:42.090 --> 17:43.227
HONEY.
COME ON.

17:43.330 --> 17:44.194
- WHAT?
